verbose_text: The recent discovery of " black " TiO 2 nanoparticles with visible and infrared absorption has triggered an explosion of interest in the application of TiO 2 in a diverse set of solar energy systems; however, what a black TiO 2 nanoparticle really is remains a mystery.
